data.description: Welcome to this Magnificent 4 level Colonial house situated on a corner lot in an award winning Blue Ribbon school district of Plainview. This is an ideal house for a potential mother-daughter setup with proper permits. This stunning house offers a high ceiling entry foyer, spacious living room with crown molding, high hats, solid wooden flooring, plenty of windows with natural sunlight, formal dining area with slider doors opening to the large wooden deck, large renovated eat-in-kitchen with granite countertops, tiled flooring, gas cooktop and double ovens, 4 large bedrooms and 3 updated full bathrooms, including a primary suite with a new spa-like bathroom and 2 walk-in closets. Legal Garage conversion with 2 rooms, full bathroom and sliding doors to backyard. Basement includes a spacious family den, wet bar and utility/laundry room. The fenced in backyard is perfect for entertainers, offering a large wooden deck, designer paved patio, in-ground heated swimming pool, a shed, and evergreen trees for privacy. Private driveway. Central AC and Gas Cooking and Heat! Excellent location!!! Conveniently located near neighborhood parks, Bethpage State Park, public transportation, schools, stores and restaurants at Plainview Commons, Plainview Hospital, and places of worship. Plainview Old Bethpage Schools. Taxes were grieved and approved for 3-4k reductions to approx. $16k for next year plus basic/enhanced star credits. Don't miss the chance to tour this exquisite home!
